								</svg>
							</a>
							<a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/25 p-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-800/50 hover:bg-blue-600/20">
