								</svg>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-6 text-blue-400">Services</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3">
							<li><a href="/services" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 inline-block">Unifi Services</a></li>
							<li><a href="/services" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200 hover:translate-x-1 inline-block">Technology Solutions</a></li>
